overview.longBusinessSummary: Enliven Therapeutics, Inc., a clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company, focuses on the discovery and development of small molecule inhibitors to help patients with cancer. The company's lead product candidates comprise ELVN-001, a small molecule kinase inhibitor which is in Phase 1 clinical trial to treat adults with chronic myeloid leukemia; and ELVN-002, a CNS penetrant and irreversible HER2 inhibitor that is in Phase 1 clinical trial for the treatment of non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC) and other HER2 driven cancers and solid tumors. The company is headquartered in Boulder, Colorado.
